      "content": "thanks for the report. wait, u mentioned a database connection issue... did u see anything specifically about the API gateway or the endpoint connectivity in those logs? i thought we were migrating some stuff but i don't see any deprecation notices on my end. did anything flag in the logs regarding the endpoint lifecycle?",
